'''Jenna Zan Arbor's secret laboratory''', located in Level One, Quad Two, Block Unit 3 on [[Simpla-12]], was where she did tests on [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] and other [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitives]] hoping to find the secret of [[The Force/Legends|the Force]]. [[Jenna Zan Arbor|Zan Arbor]] employed a guard named [[Nil]] to protect the [[Laboratory/Legends|laboratory]]. It was abandoned, however, when [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]], [[Siri Tachi/Legends|Siri Tachi]], and [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Adi Gallia/Legends|Adi Gallia]] broke in to free Masters [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]] and [[Noor R'aya]], held prisoner within it by Zan Arbor at the time.

